  {
   "question": "What is the Season 3 arena set for Holy Priest?",
   "answer": "The Vengeful Gladiator's pieces: Vengeful Gladiator's Salvation. The 2-piece and 4-piece set bonuses carry over between seasons, so partial upgrades never break your bonus."
  },
  {
   "question": "What are the rating requirements in Season 3?",
   "answer": "Season 3 introduces rating requirements: the Vengeful weapon needs 1850 team rating and the shoulders need 2000. Everything else is rating-free."
  },
  {
   "question": "How many arena points does full Season 3 gear cost?",
   "answer": "The five set pieces total roughly 8,250 arena points (helm/chest/legs 1,875 each, shoulders 1,500, gloves 1,125) plus about 3,750 for a main weapon. Use the arena points calculator to turn your weekly rating into a purchase timeline."
